item_data.name: Dermaplane Facial
item_data.description: Get ready to glow baby! This hour long facial is completely customized and tailored to your skin needs. Includes a deep double cleanse, extractions if needed, facial massage,  dermaplane, hand picked treaments, and finishing products to leave you glowy and protected! (not recommended for anyone with active acne or rosacea covering their whole face) Recommended every 4-6 weeks

item_data.name: Add on: Facial Cupping
item_data.description: An anti-aging alternative therapy solution that gives immediate results to lackluster skin while providing it with oxygen-rich blood flow and aiding in lymphatic drainage. With regular treatments you will notice an improvement in the appearance of fine lines & wrinkles, brighter skin, more even tone, decreased inflammation, regulated oil production and more. (not recommended for anyone with active acne or rosacea covering their whole face. Potential of small hickeys appearing instantly or day after receiving treatment but will fade over a couple days. Add-ons can only be selected to add-on to a facial, not by themselves!)

item_data.name: Dermaplaning
item_data.description: An exfoliating treatment that removes peach fuzz and dead skin cells to reveal smooth, bright skin. This will allow for deeper product penetration, smoother makeup application, and improvement in texture and pigmentation with regular treatments. Includes double cleanse, extractions if needed, dermaplane and finishing products. (not recommended for anyone with active acne or rosacea covering their whole face) Recommended every 4-6 weeks

item_data.name: Acne Bootcamp | Consultation and Treatment
item_data.description:
This appointment is your first step toward healthy skin! My acne Bootcamp is a 12 week holistic program consisting of a strict home care regimen and light acne peels every two weeks ($85 each). Price of home care varies ($150-200, not included in appointment price). In our first appointment we will discuss your health history and acne journey. I will perform a thorough skin analysis and prescribe you your personalized homecare regimen. 

Please stop the use of Retin-A or any other tretinoin and/or prescription topical product and book your consultation appointment at least 2 weeks out from the date you stopped using it.
